{ "type": "Feature", "properties": { "id": 1, "name": "广源闸", "direction": 130, "img": [{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250625_172817.jpg","caption":"广源闸东侧"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250625_172841.jpg","caption":"广源闸龙王庙"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250625_173241.jpg","caption":"广源闸西侧"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250625_172951.jpg","caption":"第七批全国重点文物保护单位"}], "text":"广源闸始建于元至元二十九年(1292年)，俗称豆腐闸，是元代水利工程专家郭守敬主持修建的白浮泉引水工程上的一座重要水工建筑物。该闸是元代通惠河上游的现存头闸，其结构大体分为闸门、闸墙和基础三部分。历史上广源闸不仅有调节河水流量、控制水位高低的作用，而且在闸上铺设木板、又具有桥的功能。现存有基础和闸墙及闸墙两侧共4个望水兽，仍保持桥闸一体的历史原貌。广源闸是元代至清代帝、后们出京游玩的重要转船处，是大运河遗产的见证之一，成为研究北京漕运和城市发展的重要节点。","auxiliary_storage_labeling_positionx": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positiony": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_show": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelrotation": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_family": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_fontstyle": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_size": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bold": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_italic": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_underline": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_color": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_strikeout": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_multilinealignment": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffersize": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffercolor": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bufferdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labeldistance": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_hali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_vali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_scalevisibility": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_minscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_maxscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_alwaysshow": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_calloutdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelallparts": null }, "geometry": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 116.306469725624254, 39.943732436480055 ] } },
{ "type": "Feature", "properties": { "id": 2, "name": "高梁闸", "direction": 77, "img": [{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_162013.jpg","caption":"桥西侧"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_161949.jpg","caption":"闸南侧"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_162020.jpg","caption":"绞关石"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_161445.jpg","caption":"第七批全国重点文物保护单位"}], "text": "高梁桥始建于元至元二十九年(1292年)，在和义门(今西直门)外所建，取名高梁桥，是元代水利工程专家郭守敬主持修建的白浮泉引水工程上的一座重要水工建筑物。高梁桥是北京西郊历史上一座名桥，桥下一侧为高梁闸，是高梁桥的重要组成部分。明清时期高梁桥周边古刹林立，酒肆、茶馆游客盈门，热闹非凡，为京西郊外的一道胜景。现高梁桥本体及高梁闸闸槽、绞关石等原有建筑物构件保存基本完好，是大运河遗产的见证之一，成为研究北京漕运和城市发展的重要节点。", "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positionx": 116.34462979628771, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positiony": 39.937881193578953, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_show": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelrotation": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_family": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_fontstyle": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_size": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bold": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_italic": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_underline": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_color": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_strikeout": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_multilinealignment": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffersize": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffercolor": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bufferdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labeldistance": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_hali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_vali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_scalevisibility": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_minscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_maxscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_alwaysshow": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_calloutdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelallparts": null }, "geometry": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 116.345400441591863, 39.941820116764227 ] } },
{ "type": "Feature", "properties": { "id": 3, "name": "澄清上闸", "direction": 90, "img": [{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_112255.jpg","caption":"澄清上闸和万宁桥西南侧"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_112434.jpg","caption":"桥西北"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_111207.jpg","caption":"镇水兽"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_112101.jpg","caption":"第七批全国重点文物保护单位"},{"url":"/images/sluices/IMG_20250627_112209.jpg","caption":"万宁桥桥面弧度"}], "text":"澄清上闸是元朝著名水利工程专家郭守敬为调节积水潭水位满足漕船航运需要而建造的重要水工建筑物。水闸初名海子闸，元代元贞元年(1295年)元世祖忽必烈赐名“澄清闸”。闸原为木质结构，元代至顺元年(1330年)改用石材重建，并与东侧万宁桥连为一体，成为积水潭东岸、通惠河起点处重要水上交通枢纽。历经数百年目前仍保存有闸槽、绞关石等原有建筑构件旧物。万宁桥又称海子桥同时因地近地安门(明为北安门、俗称后门)亦称后门桥。\n万宁桥为单孔石拱桥，桥两侧堤岸雕有镇水兽，是珍贵的石刻艺术品。现在清上闸与万宁桥，是大运河遗产的见证之一，成为研究北京运和城市发展的重要节点。\n万宁桥:俗称后门桥(因桥临近地安门，地安门又称后门，故名)。此桥始建于元，初为木构筑，后改石桥。万宁桥是北京旧城中轴线上的重要标志物之一。","auxiliary_storage_labeling_positionx": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_positiony": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_show": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelrotation": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_family": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_fontstyle": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_size": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bold": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_italic": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_underline": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_color": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_strikeout": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_multilinealignment": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffersize": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_buffercolor": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_bufferdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labeldistance": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_hali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_vali": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_scalevisibility": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_minscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_maxscale": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_alwaysshow": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_calloutdraw": null, "auxiliary_storage_labeling_labelallparts": null }, "geometry": { "type": "Point", "coordinates": [ 116